Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/brandonw/vim-files.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule update --init

Add plugins:

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule add http://github.com/name/plugin.git bundle/name
	git add .

--

Update plugin bundle

	cd ~/.vim/bundle/???
	git pull
